{
  "texts": [
    "By integrating smart grids and IoT systems securely, these frameworks contribute to SDG 7.",
    "Their emphasis on resilient digital infrastructure supports SDG 9 by enabling sustainable industrial practices.",
    "Furthermore, \"green cybersecurity\" protects environmentally focused systems, aiding SDG 13 through reduced energy usage and securing environmental initiatives.",
    "These adaptive systems also safeguard urban networks in smart cities, aligning with SDG 11.",
    "Finally, by fostering knowledge sharing and standardization (e.g., ISO 27001), they contribute to SDG 17 by enhancing global collaboration in cybersecurity standards."
  ]
}